data.description: Charming 2BR/2.5BA w/ bonus room New Construction home in Forsyth County. Desirable open floor plan including Master on Main, gourmet kitchen w/ white shaker cabinets, kitchen island, granite ctops, ss appliances, LVT Hardwood like floors, upgraded lighting & much more. Very low maintenance home in great location. Home to be completed end of April.  Pictures are showing what home will look like upon completion. Agent/Owner
